{"id":248,"parent_id":244,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":248,"title":"1 Peter 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"1 Pet.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Peter explains why the gospel is preached to the dead—Saints should speak as the oracles of God—The righteous will be tried and tested in all things."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.1","order":"03.23.004.25747"},["b","1"],"Forasmuch then as Christ hath suffered for us in the flesh, arm yourselves likewise with the same",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"mind"],":",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"for"],"he that hath suffered in the flesh hath ceased from",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"sin"],";"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.2","order":"03.23.004.25748"},["b","2"],"That he no longer should live the rest of",["i","his"],"time in the flesh to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"lusts"],"of men, but to the will of God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.3","order":"03.23.004.25749"},["b","3"],"For the time past of",["i","our"],"life may suffice us to have wrought the will of the Gentiles, when we walked in lasciviousness, lusts,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"excess"],"of wine,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"revellings"],", banquetings, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"abominable"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"idolatries"],":"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.4","order":"03.23.004.25750"},["b","4"],"Wherein they think it strange that ye run not with",["i","them"],"to the same excess of riot, speaking evil of",["i","you:"]],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.5","order":"03.23.004.25751"},["b","5"],"Who shall give account to him that is ready to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"judge"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"quick"],"and the dead."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.6","order":"03.23.004.25752"},["b","6"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"For"],"for this cause was the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"gospel"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"preached"],"also to them that are",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"dead"],", that they might be",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_6e"},"judged"],"according to men in the flesh, but live according to God in the spirit."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.7","order":"03.23.004.25753"},["b","7"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"But"],"the end of all things is at hand: be ye therefore sober, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"watch"],"unto prayer."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.8","order":"03.23.004.25754"},["b","8"],"And above all things have fervent charity among yourselves:",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"for"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"charity"],"shall cover the multitude of sins."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.9","order":"03.23.004.25755"},["b","9"],"Use",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"hospitality"],"one to another without",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"grudging"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.10","order":"03.23.004.25756"},["b","10"],"As every man hath received the gift,",["i","even so"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"minister"],"the same one to another, as good",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"stewards"],"of the manifold grace of God."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.11","order":"03.23.004.25757"},["b","11"],"If any man",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"speak"],",",["i","let him speak"],"as the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"oracles"],"of God; if any man minister,",["i","let him do it"],"as of the ability which God giveth: that God in all things may be glorified through Jesus Christ, to whom be praise and dominion for ever and ever. Amen."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.12","order":"03.23.004.25758"},["b","12"],"Beloved, think it not strange concerning the fiery",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"trial"],"which is to try you, as though some strange thing happened unto you:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.13","order":"03.23.004.25759"},["b","13"],"But",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"rejoice"],", inasmuch as ye are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"partakers"],"of Christ’s",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"sufferings"],"; that, when his glory shall be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"revealed"],", ye may be glad also with exceeding joy."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.14","order":"03.23.004.25760"},["b","14"],"If ye be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"reproached"],"for the name of Christ,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"happy"],["i","are ye;"],"for the spirit of glory and of God resteth upon you: on their part he is evil spoken of, but on your part he is glorified."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.15","order":"03.23.004.25761"},["b","15"],"But let none of you suffer as a murderer, or",["i","as"],"a thief, or",["i","as"],"an evildoer, or as a busybody in other men’s matters."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.16","order":"03.23.004.25762"},["b","16"],"Yet if",["i","any man suffer"],"as a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Christian"],", let him not be ashamed; but let him glorify God on this behalf."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.17","order":"03.23.004.25763"},["b","17"],"For the time",["i","is come"],"that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"judgment"],"must begin at the house of God: and if",["i","it"],"first",["i","begin"],"at us, what shall the end",["i","be"],"of them that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"obey not"],"the gospel of God?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.18","order":"03.23.004.25764"},["b","18"],"And if the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"righteous"],"scarcely be saved, where shall the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"ungodly"],"and the sinner appear?"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.19","order":"03.23.004.25765"},["b","19"],"Wherefore let them that suffer according to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"will"],"of God commit the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"keeping"],"of their souls",["i","to him"],"in well doing, as unto a faithful Creator."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.1a","order":"03.23.004.25766"},["b","1a"],["span.small","GR"],"intent, idea, thought."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.1b","order":"03.23.004.25768"},["b","1b"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Pet. 4:2 For",["i","you who have"],"suffered in the flesh",["i","should cease"],"from sin, that",["i","you"],"no longer",["i","the rest of your time in the flesh,"],"should live to the lusts of men, but to the will of God."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.1c","order":"03.23.004.25770"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"TG Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.2a","order":"03.23.004.25772"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/lust"},"TG Lust"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.3a","order":"03.23.004.25774"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temperance"},"TG Temperance"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.3b","order":"03.23.004.25776"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/rioting-and-reveling"},"TG Rioting and Reveling"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.3c","order":"03.23.004.25778"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/devil-church-of"},"TG Devil, Church of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.3d","order":"03.23.004.25780"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.5a","order":"03.23.004.25782"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.5b","order":"03.23.004.25784"},["b","5b"],["span.small","OR"],"living."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.6a","order":"03.23.004.25786"},["b","6a"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Pet. 4:6",["i","Because of this, is"],"the gospel preached to them",["i","who"],"are dead, that they might be judged according to men in the flesh, but live",["i","in the spirit"],"according to",["i","the will of"],"God."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.6b","order":"03.23.004.25788"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"TG Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.6c","order":"03.23.004.25790"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/genealogy-and-temple-work"},"TG Genealogy and Temple Work"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.6d","order":"03.23.004.25792"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"TG Hell"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation-plan-of"},"Salvation, Plan of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation-for-the-dead"},"Salvation for the Dead"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-disembodied"},"Spirits, Disembodied"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-in-prison"},"Spirits in Prison"],"."],["div",{"id":"6e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.6e","order":"03.23.004.25794"},["b","6e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.99"},"D&C 88:99"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/138.10,34"},"138:10, 34"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.7a","order":"03.23.004.25796"},["b","7a"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Pet. 4:7 But",["i","to you,"],"the end of all things is at hand …"],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.7b","order":"03.23.004.25798"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/watch"},"TG Watch"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.8a","order":"03.23.004.25800"},["b","8a"],["span.small","JST"],"1 Pet. 4:8 … for charity",["i","preventeth a"],"multitude of sins."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.8b","order":"03.23.004.25802"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/charity"},"TG Charity"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.9a","order":"03.23.004.25804"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hospitality"},"TG Hospitality"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.9b","order":"03.23.004.25806"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/motivations"},"TG Motivations"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.10a","order":"03.23.004.25808"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-magnifying-callings-within"},"TG Priesthood, Magnifying Callings within"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.10b","order":"03.23.004.25810"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stewardship"},"TG Stewardship"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.11a","order":"03.23.004.25812"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4"},"1 Thes. 2:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/2.1"},"Titus 2:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.11b","order":"03.23.004.25814"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/authority"},"TG Authority"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teaching-with-the-spirit"},"Teaching with the Spirit"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.12a","order":"03.23.004.25816"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/test"},"TG Test"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.13a","order":"03.23.004.25818"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/5.41"},"Acts 5:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.13b","order":"03.23.004.25820"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"TG Persecution"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.13c","order":"03.23.004.25822"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/suffering"},"TG Suffering"],"."],["div",{"id":"13d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.13d","order":"03.23.004.25824"},["b","13d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/66.2"},"D&C 66:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.14a","order":"03.23.004.25826"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/reproach"},"TG Reproach"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.14b","order":"03.23.004.25828"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/happiness"},"TG Happiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.16a","order":"03.23.004.25830"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/11.26.19-26"},"Acts 11:26 (19–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.17a","order":"03.23.004.25832"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment"},"TG Judgment"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.17b","order":"03.23.004.25834"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.46"},"D&C 18:46"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.18a","order":"03.23.004.25836"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.18b","order":"03.23.004.25838"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/godliness"},"TG Godliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.19a","order":"03.23.004.25840"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-will-of"},"TG God, Will of"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/4.19b","order":"03.23.004.25842"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/refuge"},"TG Refuge"],"."]]}
